Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gaw formation from North America,\Nled by Captain Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...carried out a surprise attack against\Nthe Earth Federation Headquarters at Jaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However, with the efforts of\Nthe Gundam and others...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Federation Forces fought back hard\Nand the enemy was forced to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But will Char really give up so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:02:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A Wish of War Orphans
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Point B-3! Thus far, we have\Nnothing out of the ordinary to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Just regular Zeon bombings, as usual.\N- Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point in regular reports\Nfrom a remote outpost like ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys aren't doing their patrols\Njust to earn a paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Another regular bombing, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's nothing to be concerned about.\NNow then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base's crew organization\Nwill remain as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be assigned to the\N13th Autonomous Corps of the Tianem fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now announce each of your ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Junior Grade Bright Noa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign Mirai Yashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Petty Officer 1 st Class Sayla Mass.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before we've even thought about It,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Chief Petty Officer Amuro Ray.\N- Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Petty Officer 2nd Class Kai Shiden.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Petty Officer 2nd Class Hayato Kobayashi.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't received anything like this{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What good will this do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaman Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaman Fraw Bow? Isn't she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nooo!\N- We don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me neither!\N- No way are we leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the children absolutely refuse\Nto go to the childcare center, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some expertise in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll convince those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, you should come with me.\N- Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and receive your appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu Jose has been promoted two ranks\Nfor honorable death in the line of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been appointed lieutenant junior grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All other casualties have also\Nbeen promoted two ranks. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promoted two ranks?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promoted two ranks... ?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promoted two ranks... ?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... Is that all they get?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They get promoted two ranks, and that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the end of the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What exactly are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You do nothing for us while we're fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...and afterwards you hand out ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you at least say "thank you"\Nto Mr. Ryu and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said you could dodge my blow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that again and I'll put you in solitary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you do say things that you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An occasional smack is good medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I get the message. Let's just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about Kikka and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They were told the facility has\Nlots of fun playgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So they went with the childcare officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think those kids will\Nreally be happy if they stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they'll be fine wherever they end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice.\NThey've gotta stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Little children shouldn't have to see\Npeople killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The preparations are done, Captain Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Juice! Juice! Delicious juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want soft-serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are so innocent and carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with kids being carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But all that does is make adults happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one cynical kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stick around here long enough,\Nyou'll all end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a war going on right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All I do is sit around waiting until\Nmy mother and father come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why you...!\N- Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home. I wanna go...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's coming!\N- Let's run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right! Now, Kikka. Let's run!\N- Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come back here!\NKatz! Letz! Kikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, you kids! Can't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please answer me, Kikka dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Katz! Letz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. They're kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on, Kikka.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's slippery, Katz. So be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Katz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure gave me a scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Char?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation's come a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably just a small sample\Nof what they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we doing it now? Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course...\NRamuji. Have your team set them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Akahana, our teams will head\Nto the Trojan Horse's dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! This'll be a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep running! If they catch us,\Nthey'll take us back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't run anymore!\N- Kikka! Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wanna rest!\N- Well, if we have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. This door opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It does? Okay, Kikka.\NWe'll rest here for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- How much longer?\N- Five more minutes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait! Hide!\N- Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stinky.\N- Is there nobody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look, Gundams!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So many!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's kinda different from Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, they're a lot different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh! Something's near its feet!\N- Huh? Near its feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- I saw something move.\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You imagined it. I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Something really moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It could've been a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?! A person?! Then we're in trouble.\N- L-Let's hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Run away! Run away!\N- The other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel\Nbut it'll make it tougher, Fraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd just like to see them once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- That's the childcare officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm glad I found you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kikka and the others have all run away!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think ill of us, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've set them to detonate in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're b-b-bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.\NWe're finally authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrific! Now we can go on the tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming too, right, Mr. Kai?\NTo the Gundam factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure. I'll go to take my mind off things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Bright.\NReport to the operations room at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the military for you.\NYou guys go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll enjoy it more without your superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- I did it! Katz, hurry!\N- You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- W-We gotta get rid of those bombs!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Katz! Kikka! You two look under here!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Any bombs??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Did you find any?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No good! At this rate,\Nwe'll blow up along with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna! What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- I found one!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's a bomb, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's one over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikka, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Start, engine! Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm trying, but this thing won't start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure you know\Nhow to make it move?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! It started!\NOkay, next I need to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Those voices were Katz and Letz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- We gotta go after them!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car, Katz! Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:15:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeons set some bombs!\NWe're throwing them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is... Amuro, looks like it's true.\NThese are time bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you find them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the Gundam factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Letz. Get in the other car\Nand leave the rest to me. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai! Help the kids into the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.\NOkay, Letz! You go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- C'mon!\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't be scared. On three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I told you it was fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! You're next, Kikka. There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You all did good. All yours, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! Yay! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever set these bombs\Nwill likely attack the White Base too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like Ramuji's team went all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ivanov. Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Captain Char.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Distract the enemy with the Acguys.\N- Understood, sir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to look rough up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's attacking with mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Katz!? Kikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Letz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Katz! Letz! Please answer me!\N- Kikka! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kikka!\N- Katz! Letz! Kikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Artesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I never would have thought\Nyou'd join the Zeon forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my gentle brother Casval!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you leave the military for me, Artesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla! Are you there?\NPlease answer me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Got that?\N- Casval!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?! Kikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sayla?\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard gunfire... Was there a Zeon soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a Zeon officer here on this rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we shouldn't go that way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Captain Char...\N- Ignore them. We're all leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission is a failure,\Nso we're withdrawing. Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!\NFour or five mobile suits... that's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Char...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! lvanov's Acguy\Nhas been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stop, you won't survive!\NKeep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though they're Acguys,\Nhe took out four of them all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's improved his skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,An underground water vein.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing Char, he must have\Nused that opportunity to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,However, they're guaranteed to be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the children are the future\Nof the Federation Forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...so they're brought up with great care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after what happened today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, when I consider their feelings,\NI'm not sure these kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you called them the future\Nof the Federation Forces, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...They might see a world without Zeon\Nor Federation Forces within their lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you consider that possibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our little rascals here\Naren't your average children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In all this time\Nthey've seen plenty of gunfire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they've been fighting with us\Nthrough those battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They've seen some terrible things\Neven an adult like you couldn't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And they never turned away their eyes.\NYou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- They don't wanna leave us. Right?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but they...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I suppose you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make all the necessary arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then... then... It's so wonderful!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is great!\N- Now we can keep on bickering!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, due to Char's guerrilla attack,\Nthe Earth Federation Forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...have decided to speed up\Ntheir space campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The admirals have figured out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.87,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Zeon has a high opinion\Nof the White Base's abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...and so it would make an ideal decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that\Nthe 13th Autonomous Corps...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.87,0:23:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...will specialize in decoy operations?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base takes off into space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...where an immense battlefield awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Char's relentless pursuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...eventually leads to fleet combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the approaching giant tear\Nthe mobile suit to pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NA Decoy in Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Decoy in Space
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
